vim-files
=========

Vim config files for different machines

Source by putting this function in your local .vimrc:

function! GetNetVimrc(vimrc_url)
       source $VIMRUNTIME/plugin/netrwPlugin.vim
       Nread a:vimrc_url
       let tmpfile = tempname()
       save! tmpfile
       source tmpfile
       delete(tmpfile)
       enew
endfunction

then either call the function manually or add this line to local .vimrc:
call GetNetVimrc("https://raw.github.com/AxelRiese/vim-files/master/.vimrc")

